#### 6. Redundant `CultureInfo.CurrentCulture` access (3 instances)
**Impact:** `CultureInfo.CurrentCulture` involves thread-local storage lookup. Accessed up to 3 times per `ToString()` call when once suffices.
**Files:** `DataSize.cs:L160, L171, L181`
